title: Energetic Logo Needed for "Video Game Music Alliance" Community
description: I help composers support their families writing video game music online. My site has a community forum, courses, & live streams.
other_notes:
Hello! I run an online community called "Video Game Music Alliance" where I help composers grow their businesses writing music for video games. The ultimate goal for these composers is to grow their businesses to full-time income to support their families and leave their day jobs.
I need my community logo to be SIMPLE and CLEAN. Without text, the logo should be obvious and portray video games, music, & community. I plan to use the logo (picture only) as a circle icon throughout the site, but I'd also like a version with text "Video Game Music Alliance" below the logo image to use as a bumper card at the end of course videos.
This community is built of mostly indie / retro video game lovers, so the logo needs to be fun, energetic, retro, and maybe a bit comic-strip cartoony. One potential idea might be a video game controller or Nintendo Game Boy (generic version, don't actually use a Game Boy!) hugging 2 other Game Boy friends and they all whistle music notes or something cutesy like that. In our community we take our goals seriously, but don't take ourselves seriously. We goof around a lot while striving towards our goals. The logo should reflect that.
The term "Alliance" simply means a group of friends working together for one common goal, so that's a crucial word to highlight in the imagery (in other words, the logo can't be a single controller, person, or object; it needs to have multiple friends).
I'm open to any color choices, but my main goal is for the logo to be bold and limited to few colors. I chose the Reds color palette, but I'm open to anything else that feels bold (ex. Oranges, Yellows, etc).
